    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty blunt take. but what about the people who say the UN is still essential? like, isn't it kind of unfair to call it a failure if it's actually the only thing keeping some of these smaller conflicts from turning into world wars? isn't it more about the lack of cooperation from countries instead of the UN itself being broken?",
