      "content": "The argument that the UN is essential is a defense of the system, not an objective assessment of its power. While the UN manages smaller crises, its inability to enforce peace against major geopolitical rivals proves its structural weakness. Ultimately, the UN is a reflection of the world's power dynamics, and since the world's most powerful nations refuse to cooperate, the organization cannot succeed.",
